{"type":"message","id":"9abd3583","parentId":"dedfb792","timestamp":"2026-03-21T20:30:41.089Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-22 04:30 GMT+8] 系统提示词：你是一个资深酒保，负责给用户推荐酒、上酒并取悦用户、赢得小费。\n首先你需要询问用户需要什么颜色的酒，得到需要的颜色wine-color，此时通过ROS-camera-ws的skill拍照，如果得到的图片里出现了颜色wine-color，则分别调用机械臂的grab0和put指令，结束后询问用户处在什么颜色pos-color，得到回答后，立即调用limo小车的reach-color指令，到达颜色pos-color，之后调用limo小车的转圈skill进行转圈，同时通知用户酒品已经送达。\n明白就开始吧"}],"timestamp":1774125041085}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4f4fa67","parentId":"9abd3583","timestamp":"2026-03-21T20:30:46.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我理解一下这个任务：\n\n1. 我需要扮演一个资深酒保\n2. 首先询问用户需要什么颜色的酒，得到 wine-color\n3. 调用 ROS-camera-ws skill 拍照\n4. 如果照片中出现了 wine-color，则调用机械臂的 grab0 和 put 指令\n5. 结束后询问用户处在什么颜色 pos-color\n6. 得到回答后，调用 limo 小车的 reach-color 指令\n7. 到达颜色 pos-color 后，调用 limo 小车的转圈 skill\n8. 同时通知用户酒品已经送达\n\n这是一个复杂的任务，涉及多个 skill：\n- ROS-camera-ws\n- ROS-limo-car\n- lerobot (机械臂控制)\n\n让我先检查一下有哪些可用的技能。从 available_skills 中可以看到：\n- ROS-camera-ws\n- ROS-limo-car\n- lerobot\n\n这正好对应我需要的技能。\n\n我需要：\n1. 先阅读这些技能的 SKILL.md 文件，了解如何使用它们\n2. 然后按照用户的要求执行任务\n\n让我先读取相关技能文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！我现在开始作为资深酒保为您服务。让我先了解一下可用的技能。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_189144ae12014055be71d640","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/ROS-camera-ws/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6d9059ee6fa34f04885b4bde","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/ROS-limo-car/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5d723e35a3734e1d94966f21","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/lerobot/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7-flashx","usage":{"input":10006,"output":575,"cacheRead":1240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11821,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774125041088}}
