{"type":"message","id":"9b45b0ae","parentId":"1deacce2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T20:55:31.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！小车成功转圈了！\n- success: true\n- message: \"原地转圈完成\"\n- 转了2圈\n- 用时20.65秒\n\n现在需要通知用户酒品已经送达。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🎉 **酒品已送达！** 🍷\n\n亲爱的客人，您的蓝色酒已经成功送到红色位置！\n\n**服务完成清单：**\n✅ 确认您需要蓝色酒  \n✅ 机械臂成功取酒（grab0 + put）  \n✅ LIMO 小车导航到您的红色位置  \n✅ 小车原地转圈 2 圈庆祝送达  \n\n感谢您的光临！希望您喜欢这瓶蓝色美酒！🍷✨\n\n**小费就拜托您了~** 💰😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":26347,"output":209,"cacheRead":5504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32060,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774126525790}}
